snippet.title: Amber Heard Gets All The Attention In Beverly Hills
snippet.description:
Saturday, January 7, 2017:  Amber Heard was in high demand outside a Golden Globes party held in Beverly Hills.  The star was asked questions about Johnny Depp as she smiled for photos in a stunning outfit.  X17online.com
